Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iblis itu
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.23,0:02:29.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah ayahku!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serangan sebesar ini tidak akan cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, tapi inilah akhirnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengerikan melihat seseorang\Nberubah menjadi iblis
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menjadi orang yang membunuhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin bisa tepat waktu,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku harus segera mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika tidak...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu bisa meninggalkan penyesalan\Nyang sulit dihapus.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.28,0:03:59.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyedihkan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merelakan banyak hal,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,melahap semuanya,\Ndan akhirnya menjadi iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira aku sudah lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku hanya sombong.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa melepaskan perasaanku\Nsebagai manusia,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, aku menjadi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku masih
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,sangat lemah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa aku merasa
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,sangat lelah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku berhenti berjuang,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin aku akan merasa lebih tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau dan aku sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.54,0:05:00.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada akhirnya,\Nkita memilih cara hidup kita
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,daripada perasaan kita kepada seseorang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jin... Jinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu membuatku sedikit bersemangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi masih terlalu lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kurasa tidak mengejutkan jika itu\Nminuman untuk menumbuhkan kebencian.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benci ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski Ayah sudah berubah menjadi iblis,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.50,0:06:22.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,kelemahan dalam diriku yang ingin lari\Ndan berhenti bertarung...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat membencinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.82,0:06:51.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Istrimu dilecehkan oleh iblis
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan akhirnya meninggal saat melahirkan\Niblis wanita yang dia kandung.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.66,0:06:58.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi putramu memegang tangan\Niblis wanita itu dan hilang bersamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.54,0:07:01.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kini kau sendiri menjadi iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ironis sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak perlu tahu namamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tugasku adalah memburu iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan membantaimu, Iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keperkasaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anggap ini perpisahan terakhirku denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menghabisimu dalam sekejap.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.30,0:07:47.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebelum kau merasakan sakitnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan segera mengakhiri penderitaanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu ingin menjadi lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku yakin jika aku cukup kuat,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku bisa melindungi semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi jika
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidak bisa mewujudkan keinginan itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,maka aku akan
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,mengakhiri semuanya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.18,0:08:35.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat tinggal, Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang baru saja terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang kau selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.05,0:09:16.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan... Jangan mendekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.73,0:09:23.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau melakukan ini kepada Ayah?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mendekat, Monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya itu lawan yang tangguh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.75,0:09:47.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada momen saat kupikir\Nakan lebih mudah jika aku mati saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.71,0:09:51.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya\Naku tidak akan kehilangan apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.84,0:09:56.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Melihatmu mengatakan hal seperti itu,\Nlawan ini pasti luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau masih berdiri di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu artinya sudah berakhir, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita hanya perlu\Nmenyingkirkan pelakunya sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa pelan-pelan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.16,0:10:41.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang bilang\Nkita harus segera mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kita belum istirahat berhari-hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, jangan bandingkan aku denganmu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari mulai gelap.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayolah, yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,\Nkita akan pergi ke sarang iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi di malam hari terasa lebih cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, ada yang ingin kutanyakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.48,0:11:19.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah tahu apa itu Salju Sisa, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira kau sudah tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah kau memberitahuku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana cara membuat sake?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, kau memakai nasi\Nuntuk membuat koji,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu masukkan ke air\Nuntuk difermentasi, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu agak terlalu sederhana,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi pada dasarnya itu benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Salju Sisa\Npasti dibuat seperti itu juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu bagaimana cara membuat mata air sake?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.98,0:11:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan jika kau melempar koji ke mata air,\Nitu tidak akan menjadi mata air sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak apa-apa selama bukan koji.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minuman keras gabungan merujuk
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.53,0:12:06.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,pada alkohol yang dicampur bahan-bahan\Nseperti buah, rempah, atau herba
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk menambah aroma.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.96,0:12:17.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu dicampur dengan sesuatu\Nyang mengubah orang menjadi iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.59,0:12:21.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang melakukan ini\Nadalah wanita pirang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa di dasar mata air itu
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.18,0:12:28.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada jasad seseorang\Nyang mati secara tidak wajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sanggup.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini dingin, gelap, dan aku lapar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.15,0:12:43.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir-pikir, kenapa aku ikut?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau datang jauh-jauh dari Kyoto
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk mencari tahu kebenaran\Ntentang Salju Sisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak menduga hal seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah sekarang musim dingin?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga poppy salju.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa salju?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Somegorou.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.52,0:13:14.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kali pertama mencicipi Salju Sisa,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku merasa rasanya terlalu hambar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi di saat bersamaan,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku merasakan nostalgia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nostalgia?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.82,0:13:27.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir jika itu sake yang dibuat\Ndari kebencian, rasa ini masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin bukan itu yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salju Sisa
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah sake yang dibuat\Ndari penyesalan orang mati
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan obsesi yang mereka tinggalkan\Ndi dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obsesi yang mengubah\Nmanusia menjadi iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak suka mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.47,0:13:49.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku penasaran seberapa dalam\Nkebencian mereka saat mereka mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada akhirnya,\Nitu menjadi sake yang merusak orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi jelas bukan itu\Nyang ingin disampaikan mendiang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aroma ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Somegorou.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyerah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan beristirahat di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakiku hampir copot.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.54,0:14:13.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.45,0:14:16.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sinilah manusia lemah sepertiku\Nkeluar dari panggung.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau hanya ingin seseorang menemukanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau hanya menunggu dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menghasut kebencian,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,mempermainkan hati orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan mengubah mereka menjadi iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau percaya suatu hari nanti,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,seorang pemburu iblis akan datang\Ndan menghentikanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,tubuhmu juga diambil darimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun kau sudah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,menjadi seperti ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau masih bersedia menungguku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sudah pasti,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tetap menyakitimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Penjaga Miko.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah sepantasnya aku menggunakan pedangku
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk Itsukihime.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat malam,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak hari itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,rumor tentang iblis\Ndan gangguan kekerasan telah mereda.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa masalah itu sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena sumbernya hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salju Sisa di seluruh Edo\Ntelah berubah menjadi air.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya itu menyebabkan keributan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa karena itu penduduk Edo
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,sangat gelisah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya saja dunia telah berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belakangan ini, pejabat tinggi\Ndan bangsawan tunduk kepada orang asing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, rakyat merasa gelisah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.24,0:18:24.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak bisa mempertahankan\Nkebijakan sakoku itu selamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita hanya bisa membantai iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.26,0:18:36.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gelombang zaman\Ntidak bisa kita kendalikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tampak gelisah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya memikirkan wanita pirang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu dalang di balik insiden ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau khawatir\Ndia akan mencoba sesuatu lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada gunanya memikirkan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas keramahanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kutinggalkan uangnya di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku tidak segera kembali, muridku\Nmungkin akan mulai mengkhawatirkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa, Jinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau datang ke Kyoto,\Ningatlah untuk mencariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebut saja nama "Akitsu Somegorou"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kau akan segera menemukanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mengunjungimu jika sempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau di sini, Jinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah lama tidak bertemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang, Tuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah lama tidak mampir.\NItu yang pertama, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena terjadi sesuatu belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para pelanggan kami\Ntidak datang belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang kau datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.30,0:20:06.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Miura masih datang di sore hari,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi Nona Natsu dan Tuan Zenji\Njarang datang belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah kau tak datang,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,kedaiku benar-benar sepi. Sepi sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu kake soba, siap.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penjaga kedai.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa masakanmu sedikit lebih buruk?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuahnya tidak sekuat dahulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuahnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak mengubah apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin itu hanya imajinasiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong tagihannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.78,0:20:59.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segera.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinya, bisa tunggu sebentar?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Izinkan aku berjalan denganmu sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini dingin, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang terjadi sesuatu baru-baru ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku membuatmu khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya sedikit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.32,0:21:40.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, kau pelanggan tetap kami\Nyang berharga.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan meninggalkanmu di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.18,0:22:06.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga daphne odora.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.64,0:22:08.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih ingat bunga ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.28,0:22:24.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.24,0:22:27.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga ini mekar\Nsetelah bertahan di musim dingin.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.70,0:22:30.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga yang menandakan musim semi.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.75,0:22:36.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar-benar
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,menjagaku dalam segala hal.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.61,0:23:05.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salju akan membuat semua hal\Nmenjadi putih bersih.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.11,0:23:06.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang bisa lolos.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.74,0:23:12.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski pada akhirnya meleleh\Ndan menghilang tanpa jejak,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.24,0:23:15.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,sensasi dingin itu\Nakan tetap terukir di hatimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membekas dengan kuat
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.87,0:23:19.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan dalam ke dalam hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.05,0:23:26.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama seperti kebencian.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhmu
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.80,0:23:31.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah dimanfaatkan dengan baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat malam,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Itsukihime.
